{"tid":1756022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【未來方向】黎明行動改善，開花，集會，遊行","createTime":"2019-11-26T00:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T08:31:29.000Z","uid":94771,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"361d6a7cc6ba0f091b26819542799b5a856c2a2b","tid":1756022,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T00:49:53.000Z","msg":"<strong>黎明行動</strong>，開花要有個方向<br />\n<br />\n黎明行動<br />\n唔夠人全港塞，變成擾民，只係令到人遲返工，罷唔到工<br />\n<br />\n有部份公司已經有對策，遲開工，遲收工。<br />\n影響唔到堆公司<br />\n<br />\n建議<br />\n重點針對中環，觀塘，金鍾等行政商業區。唔應該全港普及咁搞<br />\n好處係成效最大化<br />\n另一方面，做的時候一定要Humble<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>開花</strong><br />\n唔應該慢無目的，應該要定個日開花目標<br />\n達成目標應該係Be water，唔應該次次等PoPo出現為目標<br />\n<br />\n<strong>集會</strong><br />\n應該要繼續搞，正式集會，商場和你唱，光復連儂牆，和你OXY<br />\n盡量將個抗爭風氣維修，以士氣文宣為目標<br />\n<br />\n<strong>遊行</strong><br />\n搞到就搞，搞唔成都無計<br />\n盡量試搞"},{"pid":"34f3e54f59b2a0e83cd4c93e720ec42e8ac33994","tid":1756022,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T00:55:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />討論下啦，成日屌人反對<br />\n又唔討論下應該點轉變"},{"pid":"b60cd9f8910f222625076094815f22f151b276f9","tid":1756022,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:09:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6282abf4e44906b2cae217baeb789bb7f784f110","tid":1756022,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:20:18.000Z","msg":"[公投]12月2日(星期一)開展黎明行動2.0<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1755364\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1755364</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"afcc3f10bf5d08d5aa3da6deeb23c386a99a3e34","tid":1756022,"uid":156791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:20:55.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"a3a2de2f8316db4b936e458d844a7324024e659c","tid":1756022,"uid":234961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-