9-11-26T01:56:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d87296e0c888d31cfb1a92ea7ed8256aa4fe9396","tid":1756022,"uid":326665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:56:49.000Z","msg":"咪ff咁多政府會理你地啦，昨晚已經即刻上訴反蒙面法啦。根本任何和理非方法，包括選舉政府都唔會理。佢地最驚就係區區開花"},{"pid":"26471f334982c4be7995cd25d35454b873cb7112","tid":1756022,"uid":136700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:57:07.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"11c15acd7d2fe40124ec7e8f7fb38fe3b85eb66a","tid":1756022,"uid":265949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:57:44.000Z","msg":"正確，唔可以停"},{"pid":"7e46126a102623a776cecf927c0b1a93e4c040af","tid":1756022,"uid":199120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T02:10:05.000Z","msg":"食住個勢和理非非遊行最好<br />\n<br />\n好處：動搖藍絲，做下勢，提升士氣<br />\n難處：地鐵封站、popo中斷遊行，武力驅散<br />\n<br />\n其實咁多位新區議員一齊舉行<br />\n相信地鐵同popo冇咁易亂黎<br />\n<br />\n話比世界知<br />\n我地和理非一定唔會同勇武割蓆<br />\n同埋popo點樣無理對付我地嘅後生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中大理大不是condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7d5be42a6728678908d9f2fa977027b2d7b8c6","tid":1756022,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T02:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac67f2091e8772b2104bc66c33ee8e77584b15b6","tid":1756022,"uid":320078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T02:47:38.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n同埋黃色經濟圈係必須重力推行<br />\n只有經濟先可以影響到呢個仆街政府"},{"pid":"545ce04807523432e44ea7aa0464b0af5aafaf69","tid":1756022,"uid":307082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e46126a102623a776cecf927c0b1a93e4c040af","tid":1756022,"uid":199120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T02:10:05.000Z","msg":"食住個勢和理非非遊行最好<br />\n<br />\n好處：動搖藍絲，做下勢，提升士氣<br />\n難處：地鐵封站、popo中斷遊行，武力驅散<br />\n<br />\n其實咁多位新區議員一齊舉行<br />\n相信地鐵同popo冇咁易亂黎<br />\n<br />\n話比世界知<br />\n我地和理非一定唔會同勇武割蓆<br />\n同埋popo點樣無理對付我地嘅後生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中大理大不是condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T02:54:38.000Z","msg":"動搖藍絲真係好重要，就憑投比建制既總票數有增長就知唔可以輕視(唔好理幾多嚟自種票廢票買票，做人一定要謹慎)，證明我哋多咗人支持我地同時亦都多咗人支持佢哋。同一堆藍屍交手發現佢哋通常痛恨係阻人番工塞地鐵阻路行為，唔好諗住同藍屍講多哂氣，佢哋有D真係會同你同理說理(佢哋甚至認同我哋最初理念，但好嬲係我哋越嚟越過份)，如果我哋可以動搖依班肯講道理藍屍，做好埋文宣工作，立法會選舉話唔定我哋真係可以奪埋賤制既票"},{"pid":"9a46edf8bfab244169b2fff9184b767958c452c7","tid":1756022,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dZhFYAp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdZhFYAp.jpg&h=c30107b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a014894fdfdd42eaaa4158e448e05bbef51ecbb","tid":1756022,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T04:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f31f0608591416b1563c7b262c84373744dd956","tid":1756022,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:37:21.000Z","msg":"行動! 12月2日 黎明行動2.0 要文宣! 儲氣!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eBmENS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eBmENS</a>"}],"pinned":{"pid":"9a46edf8bfab244169b2fff9184b767958c452c7","tid":1756022,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26